WEEK 05 PROGRESS REPORT

EdgeCloud Monitor – Sprint 3 React Dashboard and Monitoring Visualisation

Overview

During Week 05, development focused on Sprint 3 dashboard implementation for EdgeCloud Monitor.

The main objective was to move from backend-only monitoring workflows into a working React dashboard that connects securely to the cloud-native backend through the API Gateway. This included dashboard authentication, JWT-protected routing, API Gateway CORS fixes, system overview metrics, service health visibility, edge device monitoring, and telemetry metrics visualisation.

This week established the frontend monitoring layer required to make EdgeCloud Monitor usable as an operational dashboard.

