API Gateway and CORS Fixes

A major technical issue was identified when the React dashboard attempted to call protected backend APIs through the API Gateway.

Problem encountered:

* browser requests failed due to CORS preflight rejection
* OPTIONS requests were blocked by the Gateway security layer
* React could not access protected Monitoring and Device APIs

Resolution:

* added API Gateway CORS configuration
* allowed the React frontend origin
* allowed Authorization and Content-Type headers
* allowed GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, and OPTIONS
* updated JWT filtering so browser preflight requests could pass correctly
* verified successful CORS preflight response from the API Gateway

This resolved the React to Gateway communication issue.

