Technical Challenges Encountered

CORS and Browser Preflight Requests

React requests failed even though terminal curl requests worked.

Cause:

* browsers send OPTIONS preflight requests before authenticated API calls
* the API Gateway rejected OPTIONS requests before JWT-protected requests could continue

Resolution:

* added Gateway CORS configuration
* allowed OPTIONS requests
* verified successful browser-to-Gateway communication

⸻

Stale Eureka Service Discovery Route

After rebuilding the Monitoring Service, the API Gateway attempted to call an outdated container hostname.

Error observed:

Name or service not known

Resolution:

* restarted the API Gateway
* refreshed Eureka service discovery routing
* verified Monitoring Service endpoint through the Gateway

⸻

Missing Backend API Contract

The Service Health Monitoring view required a list of monitored services, but the Monitoring Service did not expose a GET endpoint.

Resolution:

* added a monitored services list endpoint
* rebuilt and restarted the Monitoring Service
* verified the endpoint through the API Gateway
* merged the backend fix before continuing frontend integration

