Conclusion

Week 05 successfully moved EdgeCloud Monitor from backend monitoring services into a working React-based monitoring dashboard.

The platform now supports secure dashboard login, protected routing, system overview metrics, device monitoring, telemetry metrics visualisation, and live API integration through the API Gateway.

Several real cloud-native integration issues were identified and resolved, including CORS preflight failures, stale Eureka routing, and a missing Monitoring Service API contract.

This week represents a major Sprint 3 milestone because EdgeCloud Monitor now demonstrates end-to-end functionality across React, API Gateway, JWT authentication, Docker Compose, Eureka, Monitoring Service, Device Service, and MySQL-backed monitoring data.